{"tid":2240604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六點前掛八號 （訓醒就入黎啦","createTime":"2020-10-12T19:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:43:26.000Z","uid":210495,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4849db30db63f0b70d9665f5822fa7fe17c2053","tid":2240604,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T19:42:43.000Z","msg":"*緊急仲有7日就到期* 13/10/2020 2:45am update<br />\n<br />\n*聯署－要求德國聯邦議會就《港版國安法》制裁中國* 請願書<br />\n<br />\n呢個係有法律效用，夠50,000個聯署，德國國會一定會展開聽證聆訊，已簽44,219，仲有7日時間咋，之前因為只有德文和要填好繁複嘅資料，而家有手足整咗中文簡化版，快啲簽啦！🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=9fe75c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n<br />\n教學聯署：<br />\n1.） 㩒入 <a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=9fe75c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a> 後，見到「呼籲德國聯邦議會就《港版國安法》制裁中國」。<br />\n<br />\n2.）下面有：「詳情」，就㩒入去，再滑落去最底，見到「註冊並聯署」㩒入去，填上姓氏、名字、電郵，然後㩒「註冊」。<br />\n<br />\n3.）彈出一段英文，意思是使用這平台聯署要遵守的普通規則，㩒「Agree」即同意。跟住彈出「按此傳是你的郵箱」，就㩒落去。<br />\n<br />\n4.）進入你的郵箱，打開「epetitionen」，在郵件中間有德國議會條link「 <a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/epet/option/registrieren.$$$.aktion.adee4ad1-bd6e-47c4-9c5f-83ab2c6b5f38.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fepet%2Foption%2Fregistrieren.%24%24%24.aktion.adee4ad1-bd6e-47c4-9c5f-83ab2c6b5f38.html&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=97bcd165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/epet/option/registrieren.$$$.aktion.adee4ad1-bd6e-47c4-9c5f-83ab2c6b5f38.html</a> 」<br />\n就㩒入去，當入到德國議會網站，即是已成功登記。<br />\n<br />\n5.）跟住再入返 <a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition，再㩒入「詳情」，再滑落去最底，見到「藍色聯署」㩒入去，填上電郵，不用填「密碼」，然後㩒「簽署請願書」，完成。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E3%A9%92%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8C%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E6%BB%91%E8%90%BD%E5%8E%BB%E6%9C%80%E5%BA%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%8D%E3%A9%92%E5%85%A5%E5%8E%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%A1%AB%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%A1%AB%E3%80%8C%E5%AF%86%E7%A2%BC%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%BE%8C%E3%A9%92%E3%80%8C%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E6%9B%B8%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E3%80%82&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=abe480f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition，再㩒入「詳情」，再滑落去最底，見到「藍色聯署」㩒入去，填上電郵，不用填「密碼」，然後㩒「簽署請願書」，完成。</a><br />\n<br />\n6.）跟住會岀返去最先入去個頁，想知是否成功，㩒「已簽署」，再㩒「詳情」，再滑落去最底，見到一剔「藍色已簽署」 。<br />\n<br />\n****** 成功簽署 ******<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1572149309754974/posts/2439043833065513/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1572149309754974%2Fposts%2F2439043833065513%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=c74eaa11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1572149309754974/posts/2439043833065513/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n跟手有個聯署：系畀英國政府，要求賦予香港人民在英國居住的權利，哩個好易簽，順手簽埋佢啦！"},{"pid":"12bed72797e24a2354ef106fbcf682cfbc3f7d72","tid":2240604,"uid":217452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T19:43:50.000Z","msg":"Push notifications"},{"pid":"70ebd9b57c623e71540283d9d74bd32135b7fc28","tid":2240604,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T19:45:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"441ed51eb854d95c63a6f1d4f4b45de73505553a","tid":2240604,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T19:48:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ff5ab16197865767d2bb89eac23c2d9496a40c7","tid":2240604,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":